    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im on sertraline for my anxiety (50mg) but it's making me feel super nauseous and weirdly jittery all the time. i saw on a blog that st john's wort is basically the natural version of that and works just as well. can i just swap them out to avoid the side effects?",
