      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Stopping sertraline abruptly can cause withdrawal symptoms, so tapering should be done under medical supervision, not just by guessing. Even with a gap, the interaction risk remains real, and St. John's Wort can affect how your body processes other substances. Since you are waiting for a proper consultation, I strongly advise you to seek care at an urgent care clinic or nurse hotline for advice before making any changes.",
